title: Anshlavs - Discography - 2010-2012
description:
The man who the last two years of his 11-year prison term dedicated creation of IDM and experimental music. 
______________________

The project is closed due to lack of proper atmosphere. In the coming days I will leave the institution, the greatest merit of which was that it stimulated my mind to create this music. What will happen in the future, time will tell
